{ 0-0-0 will must likely transpose into this line. Black can't really take advantage of this with ...d5 so g4 can be played. White hopes to start a major attack on the kingside with g5 etc in the future. }
10... h6 11. O-O-O b5 12. Kb1 Nb6 13. Qf2 *

