12. O-O-O { White has strong pressure down the d-file. } 12... Rxc3
{ This is a very interesting exchange sacrifice. } 13. Bd2 Qxa2 14. Bxc3 g6
{ Black is preparing to activate his bishop with Bh6. } 15. b4
{ White can now control a1 with his queen. } 15... Nd5 16. Bc4
{ White is clearly better, but the position is very sharp. } *

