{ This is a thematic sicilian move. White adds support to his queenside pawns and takes his king off of the semi-open c-file. }
11... Qc7 { White seeks play down the c-file. } 12. h4
{ Now White can begin to push on the h-file. } 12... Rfc8 13. h5
